name: Ascend AI (Ongoing)
desc: Building an AI-powered personal development tool that leverages NLP, ML, and gamification to help users set and achieve their goals, build positive habits, and break negative ones, all while integrating seamlessly with existing platforms like Google Calendar.

name: Flashcard SaaS

name: Event Finder

desc: Web app built using React.js, Next.js, Firebase, Chart.js, MUI for users to track their pantry items with visualization .

name: Resume Parser
desc: This Flask web application uses Python, Flask, SQLite, and various NLP and machine learning tools to automate the screening of internship resumes by matching job descriptions with candidate resumes.

name: Helmet Detector
desc: This Flask web application uses Python, Flask, OpenCV, YOLOv8, NumPy, and Base64 for helmet detection in images and videos, automating safety verification in high-risk environments like construction sites.
